info.name: Pretty Little Liars

info.cast: Troian Bellisario, Ashley Benson, Lucy Hale, Shay Mitchell, Sasha Pieterse, Tyler Blackburn, Ian Harding, Janel Parrish

info.plot: Spencer baixa a guarda para Jonny. Emily continua tentando entender Talia. Hanna investiga Lesli, a amiga de Mona
